Why we should learn hot to read write
an excel file?
  When we perform data driven testing, we need to
  read/write data in excel files.
What do we need to know for reading the
data from any file?
1.we must know the location of the file.
2.we must know how to bring the data from the file into the
script/java code.
3.We must have a class to manipulate the file.
To get the location of file in IntelliJ we can right-click
we can click on copy path/reference.